docs.text: About Us ¶ We are mobile developers, based in Paris, working with hybrid and cross platform technologies. Our goal is to help the client's business succeed, by solving their problems together using agile and lean, and developing the best product to satisfy the client's user needs. Learn more about us in our french website .
